Description: on-screen protractor overlay for Linux
 Transparent, always-on-top protractor for measuring angles anywhere on
 your desktop. Drag the arms to measure, rotate the protractor along its
 arc, and move it freely across multiple monitors.
 .
 Designed for Ubuntu and other Debian-based systems with PyQt5.
